#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn6.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn6.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The Appeal "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Aññatarabrahmasutta → aparādiṭṭhisuttaṃ (bj, s1-3) | aparādiṭṭhi (pts1)
msgctxt "sn6.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Aññatarabrahmasutta "
msgstr "5. A Certain Brahmā "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn6.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.5:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa brahmuno evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "Now at that time a certain Brahmā had the following harmful misconception: "

msgctxt "sn6.5:1.3"
msgid "“natthi so samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā yo idha āgaccheyyā”ti. "
msgstr "“No ascetic or brahmin can come here!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.5:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassa brahmuno cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso … pe … tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi. "
msgstr "Then the Buddha knew what that Brahmā was thinking. As easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, he vanished from Jeta’s Grove and reappeared in that Brahmā realm. "

msgctxt "sn6.5:1.5"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā. "
msgstr "Then the Buddha sat cross-legged in the air above that Brahmā, having entered upon the fire element. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.315, sc2
msgctxt "sn6.5:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Mahāmoggallāna thought, "

msgctxt "sn6.5:2.2"
msgid "“kahaṃ nu kho bhagavā etarahi viharatī”ti? "
msgstr "“Where is the Buddha staying at present?” "

#. VAR: mahāmoggallāno → mahāmoggalāno (mr)
msgctxt "sn6.5:2.3"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhagavantaṃ dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisinnaṃ tejodhātuṃ samāpannaṃ. "
msgstr "With clairvoyance that is purified and superhuman, he saw the Buddha seated cross-legged in the air above that Brahmā, having entered upon the fire element. "

msgctxt "sn6.5:2.4"
msgid "Disvāna—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya, pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evameva—jetavane antarahito tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi. "
msgstr "Then, as easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, he vanished from Jeta’s Grove and reappeared in that Brahmā realm. "

#. VAR: nissāya → upanissāya (si)
msgctxt "sn6.5:2.5"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno puratthimaṃ disaṃ nissāya tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā nīcataraṃ bhagavato. "
msgstr "Then Mahāmoggallāna—positioning himself in the east, below the Buddha—sat cross-legged in the air above that Brahmā, having entered upon the fire element. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.145, sc3
msgctxt "sn6.5:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato mahākassapassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Mahākassapa … "

msgctxt "sn6.5:3.2"
msgid "“kahaṃ nu kho bhagavā etarahi viharatī”ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:3.3"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā mahākassapo bhagavantaṃ dibbena cakkhunā … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:3.4"
msgid "disvāna—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso … pe … evameva—jetavane antarahito tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:3.5"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahākassapo dakkhiṇaṃ disaṃ nissāya tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā nīcataraṃ bhagavato. "
msgstr "positioned himself in the south … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.316, sc4
msgctxt "sn6.5:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato mahākappinassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Venerable Mahākappina … "

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.2"
msgid "“kahaṃ nu kho bhagavā etarahi viharatī”ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.3"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā mahākappino bhagavantaṃ dibbena cakkhunā … pe … tejodhātuṃ samāpannaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.4"
msgid "Disvāna—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.5"
msgid "evameva—jetavane antarahito tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.6"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahākappino pacchimaṃ disaṃ nissāya tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā nīcataraṃ bhagavato. "
msgstr "positioned himself in the west … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn6.5:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato anuruddhassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Venerable Anuruddha … "

msgctxt "sn6.5:5.2"
msgid "“kahaṃ nu kho bhagavā etarahi viharatī”ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:5.3"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā anuruddho … pe … tejodhātuṃ samāpannaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:5.4"
msgid "Disvāna—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso … pe … tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:5.5"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā anuruddho uttaraṃ disaṃ nissāya tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā nīcataraṃ bhagavato. "
msgstr "positioned himself in the north, below the Buddha, sitting cross-legged in the air above that Brahmā, having entered upon the fire element. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn6.5:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno taṃ brahmānaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Mahāmoggallāna addressed that Brahmā in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn6.5:7.1"
msgid "“Ajjāpi te āvuso sā diṭṭhi, "
msgstr "“Sir, do you still have the same view "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:7.2"
msgid "Yā te diṭṭhi pure ahu; "
msgstr "that you had in the past? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:7.3"
msgid "Passasi vītivattantaṃ, "
msgstr "Or do you see the radiance "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:7.4"
msgid "Brahmaloke pabhassaran”ti. "
msgstr "transcending the Brahmā realm?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.1"
msgid "“Na me mārisa sā diṭṭhi, "
msgstr "“Good sir, I don’t have that view "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.2"
msgid "yā me diṭṭhi pure ahu; "
msgstr "that I had in the past. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.3"
msgid "Passāmi vītivattantaṃ, "
msgstr "I see the radiance "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.4"
msgid "brahmaloke pabhassaraṃ; "
msgstr "transcending the Brahmā realm. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.5"
msgid "Svāhaṃ ajja kathaṃ vajjaṃ, "
msgstr "So how could I say today "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.6"
msgid "ahaṃ niccomhi sassato”ti. "
msgstr "that I am permanent and eternal?” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.146, pts2ed1.317, sc9
msgctxt "sn6.5:9.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā taṃ brahmānaṃ saṃvejetvā—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya, pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evameva—tasmiṃ brahmaloke antarahito jetavane pāturahosi. "
msgstr "Having inspired a sense of awe in the Brahmā, as easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, the Buddha vanished from the Brahmā realm and reappeared in Jeta’s Grove. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.5:9.2"
msgid "Atha kho so brahmā aññataraṃ brahmapārisajjaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then that Brahmā addressed a member of his retinue, "

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.3"
msgid "“ehi tvaṃ, mārisa, yenāyasmā mahāmoggallāno tenupasaṅkama; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ evaṃ vadehi: "
msgstr "“Please, good sir, go up to Venerable Mahāmoggallāna and say to him: "

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.4"
msgid "‘atthi nu kho, mārisa moggallāna, aññepi tassa bhagavato sāvakā evaṃmahiddhikā evaṃmahānubhāvā; "
msgstr "‘Moggallāna my good sir, are there any other disciples of the Buddha who have power and might "

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.5"
msgid "seyyathāpi bhavaṃ moggallāno kassapo kappino anuruddho’”ti? "
msgstr "comparable to the masters Moggallāna, Kassapa, Kappina, and Anuruddha?’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.5:9.6"
msgid "“Evaṃ, mārisā”ti kho so brahmapārisajjo tassa brahmuno paṭissutvā yenāyasmā mahāmoggallāno tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "“Yes, good sir,” replied that retinue member. He went to Moggallāna and asked as instructed. "

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.7"
msgid "“atthi nu kho, mārisa moggallāna, aññepi tassa bhagavato sāvakā evaṃmahiddhikā evaṃmahānubhāvā; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.8"
msgid "seyyathāpi bhavaṃ moggallāno kassapo kappino anuruddho”ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.5:9.9"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno taṃ brahmapārisajjaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Mahāmoggallāna addressed that member of Brahmā’s retinue in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "sn6.5:10.1"
msgid "“Tevijjā iddhipattā ca, "
msgstr "“There are many disciples of the Buddha "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:10.2"
msgid "cetopariyāyakovidā; "
msgstr "who have the three knowledges, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:10.3"
msgid "Khīṇāsavā arahanto, "
msgstr "and have attained psychic power, expert in reading minds, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:10.4"
msgid "bahū buddhassa sāvakā”ti. "
msgstr "they’re perfected ones with defilements ended.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn6.5:11.1"
msgid "Atha kho so brahmapārisajjo āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā anumoditvā yena so brahmā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā taṃ brahmānaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then that member of Brahmā’s retinue, having approved and agreed with what Mahāmoggallāna said, went to that Brahmā and said to him, "

msgctxt "sn6.5:11.2"
msgid "“āyasmā, mārisa, mahāmoggallāno evamāha: "
msgstr "“Good sir, Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said this: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "sn6.5:12.1"
msgid "‘Tevijjā iddhipattā ca, "
msgstr "‘There are many disciples of the Buddha "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:12.2"
msgid "cetopariyāyakovidā; "
msgstr "who have the three knowledges, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:12.3"
msgid "Khīṇāsavā arahanto, "
msgstr "and have attained psychic power, expert in reading minds, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:12.4"
msgid "bahū buddhassa sāvakā’”ti. "
msgstr "they’re perfected ones with defilements ended.’” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "sn6.5:13.1"
msgid "Idamavoca so brahmapārisajjo. "
msgstr "That’s what that member of Brahmā’s retinue said. "

msgctxt "sn6.5:13.2"
msgid "Attamano ca so brahmā tassa brahmapārisajjassa bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, that Brahmā was happy with what the member of his retinue said."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
